To sign a chart, use the '--sign' flag. In most cases, you should also provide '--keyring path/to/secret/keys' and '--key keyname'. $ helm package --sign ./mychart --key mykey --keyring ~/.gnupg/secring.gpg If '--keyring' is not specified, Helm usually defaults to the public keyring unless your environment is otherwise configured.
